    "There are several algorithms that can be employed to construct the decision tree including ID3 (Goodfellow et al., 2016), C4.5 (Quinlan, 1985), and Classification and Regression Trees (CART) (Quinlan, 1993).",
    "The Scikit-Learn library (Berk, 2020) that uses the CART algorithm which constructs the binary tree to form a predictor was implemented in the present study.",
